Data extraction was conducted by the lead author (DAP) and independently reviewed by (ARZ) and (JFTA) to ensure accuracy and reliability. To facilitate comparisons between study groups, effect measures for continuous outcomes were collected, including mean and standard deviation (mean ± SD), mean and standard error (mean ± SE), median and interquartile range (median [IQR]), and log-transformed values of circulating inflammatory markers at baseline. Prior to analysis, data using the formula SD = SE x \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
